    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Laguna Seca Blue. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a 25% locking limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless: the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearing service is fully documented. Suspension remains taut with factory-spec bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis maintains its original torsional rigidity. No pixel degradation in the cluster; zero bolster wear on the Nappa leather. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
