    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a factory-fresh finish with a deep, mirror-like luster and zero road imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather retains its original scent and supple texture, free from any creasing or sun damage. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver-assist features, functions with surgical precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule documented by a complete, chronological service history. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of single-owner, adult care, this car offers the tactile and visual experience of a brand-new vehicle. It comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover.",
